data.description: This charming single story home situated on a sprawling acre of land within a private boutique community, offers the perfect blend of privacy, comfort and rustic charm. Step inside, and notice the craftsmanship and attention to detail featuring upscale finishes throughout. The spacious open and airy living area features a stone fireplace, creating a cozy ambiance and windows flood the room with abundance of natural light. Beautiful tile flooring throughout. The living area seamlessly connects the kitchen, boasting trendy white cabinetry, ample counter space, equipped with stainless steel appliances, walk in pantry, additional storage closet and expansive granite island a focal point for entertaining. Work from home in style within the dedicated study, providing a space for focus and productivity. The master suite is complete with tray ceiling, en-suite bathroom that offers the ultimate in comfort and luxury. Master bath features dual vanity, soaking tub and separate walk in shower and expansive walk in closet. Three additional bedrooms offer flexibility for guests accommodations, family, or creative use, ensuring everyone has their own space. Enjoy the Texas outdoors featuring a extended back patio, outdoor kitchen an ideal spot for outdoor dining, entertaining guests, or simply unwinding while taking in the serene views to include a designated fire pit to gather around. Massive outdoor 2,400 sq ft workshop provides abundance space for your hobbies, projects and equipment with a dedicated road making parking a RV very accessible. Equipped with the latest upgrades in insulation, climate control, electric vehicle charging, storage solutions, workbenches to include two 14x14 garage doors ensuring that all your outdoor recreational and vehicles have a secure, convenient place to call home. This remarkable property has it all and offers the rare opportunity to own a piece of tranquility and experience the perfect blend of comfort, style, and functionality.
